original_title: Johannes Brahms - Karol Szymanowski - Symphonies No2 (London Symphony Orchestra)
overview: Valery Gergiev conducts the London Symphony Orchestra in recorded at Barbican Hall, London in 2012. The concert opens with Brahms's Tragic Overture, Op. 81 followed by Karol Szymanowksi's Symphony No. 2, Op. 19. The concert closes with Brahms's Symphony No. 2, Op. 73. Dirección	Laurent Lesperon Elenco	Valery Gergiev, Karol Szymanowski, Johannes Brahms Géneros	Videos musicales y conciertos Subtítulos	No disponible Idiomas de audio	English
